      <DIV class="FAQ" onclick="toggle('faq2')">
       <ul><li>what is SQL Injection?</li></ul>
      <div id="faq2" class="FAA"><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>
       SQL injection is one of the most common web attack mechanisms utilized by attackers to steal sensitive data from organizations. While SQL Injection can affect any data driven application that uses a SQL database, it is most often used to attack web sites.

      </div>
      </DIV>

      <DIV class="FAQ" onclick="toggle('faq3')">
        <ul><li>Does MongoDB support transactions?</li></ul>
      <div id="faq3" class="FAA"><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>
      MongoDB does not support multi-document transactions. However, MongoDB does provide atomic operations on a single document.
